{"tid":948760,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得做節啲餸好難食?","createTime":"2018-12-20T10:01:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-21T02:29:22.000Z","uid":59312,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0f7d2c279b98c9e32b5b4b12072df57fdb2fe2bd","tid":948760,"uid":59312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T10:01:02.000Z","msg":"拜完神擺左大半日乾爭爭嘅白切雞同燒肉<br />\n啲汁杰撻撻嘅髮菜豉<br />\n油到仆街嘅老火湯<br />\n蒸到過哂火要咬好耐嘅魚<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果係自己屋企煮成咁我會叫佢地出街食算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但而家係外家煮成咁，仲要好自豪咁話又抵又好味，好過出街食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食唔哂仲要我pack飯第二日返工做lunch<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"457ee1c7700ea14c8b5bf5f3d6a74e57b5f07520","tid":948760,"uid":107364,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T10:09:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a5a4188fc3d0f65ad726073a40fdc26ea140548b","tid":948760,"uid":59312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"457ee1c7700ea14c8b5bf5f3d6a74e57b5f07520","tid":948760,"uid":107364,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T10:09:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T10:48:57.000Z","msg":"煮得好食我會食呀<br />\n問題係煮得難食又冇人敢出聲仲要叫你帶多餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11353c537b9ffa7217a3d52b12b30824ac9ebbe4","tid":948760,"uid":107364,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T10:54:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2ff39db2ec9b543e49bf4d1e67c7b4988fb0b24a","tid":948760,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T11:05:29.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過係你屋企人on9<br />\n連條魚都蒸唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10dd6b67689b7389b47e372fa1aead433fa96220","tid":948760,"uid":59312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2ff39db2ec9b543e49bf4d1e67c7b4988fb0b24a","tid":948760,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T11:05:29.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過係你屋企人on9<br />\n連條魚都蒸唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T11:17:42.000Z","msg":"煮得差係一個因素<br />\n但做節餸對比起平時啲家常菜或者大牌檔式小炒的確係冇咁吸引(至少對我黎講)"},{"pid":"ad4e4ffd57f570a61cb0385482951a3d237e8630","tid":948760,"uid":7125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T11:17:55.000Z","msg":"咁你煮唔好姐 關個廚師事 唔關啲餸本身事播"},{"pid":"bdee83515f1041170ec7802955ecc0fd6a81c224","tid":948760,"uid":18479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T11:19:07.000Z","msg":"咁樓主你都可以煮返一兩味架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a51b032a5c4001589c1485571f97765aca198a8","tid":948760,"uid":32723,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bdee83515f1041170ec7802955ecc0fd6a81c224","tid":948760,"uid":18479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T11:19:07.000Z","msg":"咁樓主你都可以煮返一兩味架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T13:13:13.000Z","msg":"仲帶飯！？<br />\n<br />\n渣架<br />\n<br />\n倒哂佢啦隔夜餸無營養呀"},{"pid":"a8ea223d48e08d6e72a24f588fd2f100b67f5846","tid":948760,"uid":43856,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T19:09:07.000Z","msg":"睇嚟樓主由細到大都未食過一餐好食嘅做節飯<br />\n陰尻公<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae40390b17f7fbabbced4a6a3b42711b5682907f","tid":948760,"uid":64398,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T02:29:22.000Z","msg":"煮果個煮得差姐 <br />\n7成熟白切雞 , 髮菜蓮藕炆豬手豬脷  , 清蒸多寶魚 加多煲花膠魚翅湯. <br />\n不知幾撚正"}]}